# Development Environment

## softwares/ tools required

* Docker
* Browsers - Firefox/chrome
* Jetbrains tool box (used to install jetbrains tools example phpstorm)
* IDE - phpstrom
* typora
* git
* cpanel

## Directories

* cpanel app folder - $HOME/cpanel
* projects folder - $HOME/projects
* project root folder - $HOME/projects/{project-core}/{project-core}-{project-version}
    ** example $HOME/projects/gnt/gnt-1.0.0
* documents folder $HOME/documents
    ** example for php tutorials - $HOME/documents/php
    ** example for yii2 tutorials - $HOME/documents/yii2
    ** example for software testing tutorials - $HOME/documents/software-testing

## read the follwoings before start

* Docker

## setup environment

* install required softwares
    * You can install all softwares via pamac
    * install php storm via jetbrains toolbox
    * Do Docker post installtion steps after docker installtion
* setup cpanel app

